official_title: Acceptance and Completion Rate of Free HPV Vaccination Among Underserved Adult Patients (Age 18-45)
inclusion_criteria:
* Male and female adults patients seen at Volunteers in Medicine ages 18-45 years of age who read and understand English or Spanish
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 45 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Children (under 18 years of age)
* Individuals who had previously received any dose of HPV vaccine
